TITLE: Optimizing React Components with useMemo and useCallback
DESCRIPTION: This React functional component demonstrates the use of `useMemo` to cache the result of a computation (`requirements`) and `useCallback` to cache a function (`handleSubmit`). Both hooks take a dependency array to re-evaluate only when specific values change, preventing unnecessary re-renders of child components like `ShippingForm`.

SOURCE: https://react.dev/reference/react/useCallback

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
